<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She recently went public with new boyfriend Brandon Myers after weeks of claiming they were just friends.</p>

<p>And Gabby Allen looked on cloud nine as she shared a series of loved-up snaps with her beau on Instagram on Tuesday.</p>

<p>The former Love Island star, 28, posted a photo of Brandon giving her a kiss on the forehead as they leaned in close.</p>

<p>Couple: Gabby Allen, 28, looked on cloud nine as she shared a series of loved-up snaps with her boyfriend Brandon Myers, 24, on Instagram on Tuesday</p>

<p>Gabby looked sensational in the post, donning a crisp white shirt and a pair of gold earrings along with a light pallet of makeup.</p>

<p>The reality star completed her look by styling her platinum blonde tresses into loose waves for the snaps. </p>

<p>Former Ex On The Beach star Brandon sported a gold shirt and a grey vest while Gabby captioned the post with a simple: '❤️'.</p>

<p>Gabby recently went Instagram official with Brandon following weeks of speculation about their romance. </p>

<p>Romance: The former Love Island star posted a photo of Brandon giving her a kiss on the forehead as they leaned in close</p>

<p>Only recently, the reality star shared a Q&amp;A to her Instagram stories in which she revealed how her relationship with the Ex On The Beach hunk 'puts everything into perspective'.</p>

<p>Gabby was asked: 'How did you know you were ready for another relationship after your last one?'</p>

<p>The reality star responded: 'I didn't. It was a slow burner. But this is VERY different to any relationship I've been in before.</p>

<p>Confirmed: Gabby recently confirmed and went Instagram official with new boyfriend Brandon after weeks of speculation</p>

<p>'It puts most of my others to shame and I can't believe what I put up with to how well I am respected and how loved I feel now.</p>

<p>'It puts everything into perspective when someone treats you right.'</p>

<p>Gabby was dating Rak-Su star Myles until August 2019, when she accused him of cheating on her, and also dumped her Love Island beau Marcel Somerville in February 2018 when she discovered he'd been unfaithful.</p>

<p>Ex: Gabby was dating Rak-Su star Myles until August 2019, when she accused him of cheating on her (pictured in happier times)  </p>
